# Authority boundary
# - CODEOWNERS routes GitHub review requests. It is not a StewardshipAssignment,
#   ReviewRecord, PolicyDecision, release approval, publication authority, or
#   proof that review occurred.
# - @bartytime4life is the only owner identity asserted here because that
#   account was verified with repository admin permission during this update.
# - Add or replace owners only after verifying that each user or team exists,
#   has explicit write access, and has an approved responsibility assignment.
# - Governance role names such as docs steward, policy steward, sensitivity
#   reviewer, or release authority are not GitHub identities. Do not encode
#   placeholder roles or unverified teams as executable owners.
# - Branch protection, rulesets, required code-owner review, and independent
#   author/approver separation remain separate controls and NEEDS VERIFICATION.
#
# Pattern order matters: the last matching pattern takes precedence.

